{"tid":2441672,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次租工廈","createTime":"2021-03-11T00:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T07:30:29.000Z","uid":153943,"like":2,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e0fa9d1bcf6a97e56fdb4a35bec380292e39363f","tid":2441672,"uid":153943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:32:28.000Z","msg":"第一次乜都唔識咁係細行租左個工廈單位，<br />\n<br />\n個經紀完全無講過佣金係幾多，直至琴日朋友問我，<br />\n<br />\n我先睇清楚張臨時合約原來上面寫要比一個月金額做佣金<br />\n<br />\n我一直都以為最多都係比半個月既姐...之後上網睇其他人講 ，多數大行就真係要收一個月既 ，但係細行個d係有價講..普遍一半都得架啦 <br />\n<br />\n之後我打去問個經紀，佢話同我講過啦 ，可能你唔記得炸嘛 <br />\n<br />\n其實好擺明就係見我咩都唔識，所以隻字都無題過 <br />\n<br />\n而家事後感覺比人呃左咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真其實要住工廈都已經好慘，你話半個月佣 一個月佣個幾千蚊對大多數人講都唔係差好遠 ，但對我黎講已經夠買一堆2手傢私電器黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n但係而家講咩都無用 ，只係可以當買個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹呻下  希望唔好出現下一個我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc72a073d02ade142f360e970c3db767e4f2c42","tid":2441672,"uid":51920,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:35:05.000Z","msg":"咁你想點 免費幫你做野好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4362bca4f6d0b39a6dd37c8ddce2df9ac6233237","tid":2441672,"uid":53798,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"你唔識字？<br />\n<br />\n比錢簽名前講個信字？"},{"pid":"e4f7f77088ad8448f41ddd09c28a3bbd8f59eb42","tid":2441672,"uid":321757,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"下次睇清楚合約先簽啦"},{"pid":"455e4858a554318979032daa8bc38346c441fbd7","tid":2441672,"uid":153943,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"3dc72a073d02ade142f360e970c3db767e4f2c42","tid":2441672,"uid":51920,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:35:05.000Z","msg":"咁你想點 免費幫你做野好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"咁我又唔係話唔比 但係覺得佢收太多姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呻下姐"},{"pid":"45f4530995aacb4c31220e939fe107567557448f","tid":2441672,"uid":353267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:38:24.000Z","msg":"你末簽講半個月一定得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee87ac6d139c916c7a8ae55452eb843e7b9c762","tid":2441672,"uid":56550,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:38:36.000Z","msg":"雖然你覺得自己好慘<br />\n但係實際上一個月 兩個月按係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2835c77b5e62452fdd7f9bcec549cfceba7a834","tid":2441672,"uid":353267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:38:47.000Z","msg":"個個後生都租 好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7820361f9143f72fce491be892a4415946908248","tid":2441672,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:40:40.000Z","msg":"當買個教訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簽字都唔逐隻字睇清楚"},{"pid":"c862eac8a2977ed158c4be8e120403b79e614420","tid":2441672,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:41:18.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你窮咩,又唔睇清楚租約寫乜,怪得邊個"},{"pid":"d9b6015084abbbdf0a6dc2fa617ca756a9ba91e7","tid":2441672,"uid":153943,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"e4f7f77088ad8448f41ddd09c28a3bbd8f59eb42","tid":2441672,"uid":321757,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"下次睇清楚合約先簽啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"份野好長  ，d字又細隻， 然後個經紀同佢d同事又係咁講呢d單位好搶手 唔租就無架啦  我只係睇左個大概就簽左<br />\n<br />\n追根究底 都係我無睇清楚既錯 下次我唔會架啦 <img src=\